Ravi Coltrane was born on the 6th of August 1965 on Long Island, New York and was the second eldest son in the family.
After the death of John Coltrane in 1967, Alice Coltrane moved the family to Los Angeles.
Tragedy struck the family again in 1982 when his older brother John Coltrane Jr. died in a car accident at the age of 17.
